<html>
<style>
	.card {
  box-shadow: 0 5px 8px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  transition: 0.3s;
  border-radius: 5px;
  padding: 5px 16px;
  margin: 10px;
}

.card:hover {
  box-shadow: 0 8px 16px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
}

.card_wrapper {
  grid-column: 3 / -3;

  margin-top: 50px;
  margin-bottom: 50px;

  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  justify-content: space-around;
  align-items: center;
}

.reasons {
  color: black;
}

.features .card_wrapper {
  align-items: flex-start;
}

.features .card {
  background-color: #2f3136;

  height: 80px;
  width: 420px;
  margin: 10px 10px;
  margin-top: 20px;
}

.reasons .card {
  color: white;

  border: 3px;
  border-style: solid;
  border-color: #7289da;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 12px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);

  max-width: 250px;
  min-height: 170px;
}

.statistics_card {
  background-color: #4c69d4;

  color: white;
  box-shadow: 2px 9px 12px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);

  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  justify-items: center;
  grid-auto-flow: row dense;

  transition: 0.1s;

  min-width: 450px;
  margin: 10px;
  padding: 10px;

  text-align: center;
}

.statistics_date {
  transition: 0.2s;
  opacity: 0;
  grid-column: 2 / -1;
  margin: -5px;
  font-size: small;
}

.statistics_card:hover .statistics_date {
  opacity: 1;
}

.statistics_card:hover {
  transform: scale(1.05);
}

.coin {
  grid-column: 2 / -1;
  border-bottom: 2px;
  border-bottom-color: black;
  border-bottom-style: solid;

  width: 95%;
  text-align: center;
  margin: 5px;
}
</style>
<body>
	<title>Tipbot.info - Multiplatform Tipbot</title>
	<div class="reasons card_wrapper">
		<div class="card">
			<h4>State of the Art Security</h4>
			<p>We only store as many coins as required for daily operation onsite. The rest of the coins are stored offsite. This means, that even in the unlikely event of a breach, our loss is limited.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="card">
			<h4>Free to use</h4>
			<p>The bot is <b>100%</b> free to use, you only pay the network fee on withdrawal</p>
		</div>
		<div class="card">
			<h4>High Availability</h4>
			<p>We strive for an uptime of over 99%</p>
			<p>If we're unable to meet this for a longer time period, we'll give everyone a month of premium free of charge</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="statistics card_wrapper">
		<div class="statistics_card">
			<picture class="coin_logo">
				<source srcset="/img/dogecoin.webp" type="image/webp">
				<img src="/img/dogecoin.png" alt="Dogecoin Logo">
			</picture>
			<div class="coin">
				<h2>Dogecoin</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="stats">
				<div class="key">tipped</div>
				<div class="value">≫ 1.500.000</div>
			</div>
			<div class="stats">
				<div class="key">rained</div>
				<div class="value">≫ 1.000.000</div>
			</div>
			<div class="stats">
				<div class="key">soaked</div>
				<div class="value">≫ 120.000</div>
			</div>
			<div class="statistics_date">
				Updated December 2018
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="statistics_card">
			<picture class="coin_logo">
				<source srcset="/img/electra.webp" type="image/webp">
				<img src="/img/electra.png" alt="Electra Logo">
			</picture>
			<div class="coin">
				<h2>Electra</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="stats">
				<div class="key">tipped</div>
				<div class="value">≫ 14.000.000</div>
			</div>
			<div class="stats">
				<div class="key">rained</div>
				<div class="value">≫ 26.000.000</div>
			</div>
			<div class="stats">
				<div class="key">soaked</div>
				<div class="value">≫ 100.000</div>
			</div>
			<div class="statistics_date">
				Updated December 2018
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="features card_wrapper">
		<div class="card">
			<h4>Multiple Currencies</h4>
			There are tip bots available for <a href="https://dogecoin.com/">Dogecoin</a> and <a href="https://electraproject.org/">Electra</a><br>
			<small>If you're interested in a tip bot for a other currency, <a href="https://contact.tipbot.info">get in touch with us</a></small>
		</div>
		<div class="card">
			<h4>Engage with your community</h4>
			Reward active users using <code>rain</code>, or distribute crypto among all online users using <code>soak</code>
		</div>
		<div class="card">
			<h4>Support</h4>
			If you run into any issues, we'll try to resolve your issue within 48h. Simply join our <a href="https://contact.tipbot.info">Support Guild on Discord</a>
		</div>
		<div class="card">
			<h4>Already trusted by</h4>
			≫ 18.000 Users<br> ≫ 1200 Guilds
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="coins card_wrapper">
		<span class="card">DOGE</span>
		<span class="card">BTC</span>
	</div>
</body>
</html>